                              "fill": "#c0c0d0",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "Overhaul the authentication system to support OAuth2, magic links, and passkeys. The current session token storage doesn't meet compliance requirements.\n\nScope:\n- Replace the auth middleware with a new implementation using JWT + refresh tokens\n- Add OAuth2 providers (Google, GitHub, Microsoft)\n- Implement magic link email authentication\n- Add passkey/WebAuthn support\n- Migrate existing user sessions to the new token format\n- Update all API endpoints to use the new auth guards\n- Write comprehensive integration tests for each auth method",
                              "lineHeight": 1.7,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
